      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AVA LEANNE (2) had a tough barrier last start so prepared to forgive that result. Good effort for second from this barrier when resuming at this circuit and distance prior and should be close to peak fitness now. SPECTA (1) is a newcomer to the Maguire yard from Victoria. Hasn't raced since March but has trialled and gets the ace draw so could make an immediate impact. ARENDELLE (3) put the writing on the wall when runner-up from a wide barrier here last time and is better served by this draw. GEOFFREY BEE (10) has been hard to fault of late. Came from this row for a win at Young last month then backed it up at his latest appearance at this venue, getting home by 2.4 metres. Player with even luck.",
